<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Sayfa Bulunamadı</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f8fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 120px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #4a90e2;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #777;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background-color: #357ab7;
        }

        .illustration {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Sayfa Bulunamadı</h2>
        <p>Üzgünüz, aradığınız sayfa mevcut değil veya taşınmış olabilir.</p>
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">Ana Sayfaya Dön</a>
        <img src="../public/images/404.jpg" alt="404" class="illustration">
    </div>
</body>

</html>
